title: Kung Fu Fighting with Jean Grae
description: Guest Bailiff Jean Grae returns to help Judge Hodgman clear out the docket, ruling on teenage liars, snuggling with teddy bears, sopping up messes with toilet paper, and more.
author: shows@maximumfun.org (Jesse Thorn)
